<bibRefCitation author="Matsumura, S." box="[425,632,1872,1898]" pageId="93" pageNumber="94" refId="ref74972" refString="Matsumura, S. (1912) Thousand Insects of Japan. Supplement IV. Keiseisha, Tokyo, 1 p. + 247 pp., 14 pls., 2 + 2 pp. [in Japanese and English]" type="book" year="1912">Matsumura (1912)</bibRefCitation>
described 
